{"tid":1675663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港教育制度咁多年都咁垃圾","createTime":"2019-10-26T04:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T10:14:28.000Z","uid":115613,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"11914c6a01b00e3e55ec8c815d5edd1b93d9c3b1","tid":1675663,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"首先學校同家長由細到大一味灌輸畀啲仔女聽<br />\n讀唔成書入唔到U會沒出息搵唔到好工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港依種填鴨式教育一味水人讀理科 商科 同啲19文學死背做考試機器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班教畜對成績好果啲叫人諗夢想<br />\n搞到學生仲on99發夢想做文學家科學家入u去讀啲19 science 出黎社會乞食<br />\n<br />\n讀書唔叻果啲又唔會guide人學下一門手藝<br />\n對比入大學將來做成世打工仔<br />\n其實創業搞下飲食依d小生意都還可以<br />\n<br />\n結果呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一班80 90 後咪出黎反抗政府lol<br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？ <br />\n因為80 90 後根本沒野可以輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話係香港撕裂係政府欠左班香港做80 90 後<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f238340b1bb653c8f12d60c8e5b41fb4469c75","tid":1675663,"uid":249015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"你個演奏會開始未"},{"pid":"28afcf8996bfee113fc359f9e77d49e80658b51d","tid":1675663,"uid":115613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"00f238340b1bb653c8f12d60c8e5b41fb4469c75","tid":1675663,"uid":249015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"你個演奏會開始未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:59:09.